	$LF
	"It gives Kunitsuna just at the right time when the wandering Beam Skeleton powers a new 0HP.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"SLEEP and get ready to warp out of this nightmare area of luck manipulation.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=3rdContinue 
	" 3rd Continue
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Showtime!
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Soma falls down, regains HP and then bumps at the "roof" of the entrance room of the Arena, which triggers a warp to the next area. 
	$LF
	"Tasty Meat is used instead of Giant Worm Soul in this process because I need to abuse damage-invincibility later, 
	$LF
	"at which point Giant Worm won't recover enough HP.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The Mind Up is used too by the way for recovering some MP.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=IronGolemroomandHippogriffSoulroomofTopFloor 
	" Iron Golem room and Hippogriff Soul room of Top Floor
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
